{"tid":1630291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修可以停一停 等人權法過咗先","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:18.000Z","uid":56394,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d7924bf15ac15e37e4fbf5c1bbaa5a37cb6d8530","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"好簡單 你覺得中共怕人權法定係怕你裝修？<br />\n唔使問都知係人權法啦下話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係why not both?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家要停嘅原因係因為美國人其實無講過核彈都唔割<br />\n而眾所鳩知美國係左膠大國<br />\n不斷裝修其實佢地只會睇到個畫面而唔知裝修個理念<br />\n所以扮下野等佢地過埋人權法再裝修都未遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465d6767e0430b48b9788628ffdbbb133ad05dae","tid":1630291,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6bc31af01570ea79825bb736866fd6cba54df962","tid":1630291,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間"},{"pid":"741eafa5a58d4860986ad86c348458af15f9c956","tid":1630291,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3e347726c4aaccc00568d564b282060f965330","tid":1630291,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56d57586ee838f8918b4b4739c46877114202e60","tid":1630291,"uid":150466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22837886e979aa928ed5047aec1c8abf1e929074","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"諗諗人權法"},{"pid":"9c9a79d06a3955ac8ef9618836e18ad9fdbaa2e8","tid":1630291,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"忍一忍手先"},{"pid":"f24ec478c4e57e414679c16ac578b7b33eb70613","tid":1630291,"uid":199858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48417aa02b4b71f3ec2ef5cc7212731104463e34","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"先人權法 再裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9abc7cd137ec5ec1493d0c93494cb0d74d02819","tid":1630291,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:16.000Z","msg":"等選埋區議會先，否則有藉口取消選舉"},{"pid":"4e5da9a30466aac5a22b9c799b079963beae5cc3","tid":1630291,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srUmzHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrUmzHb.jpg&h=306f0e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n刪app最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b72d2c1470ab054d9fe0a7d49ccd9ab45165738","tid":1630291,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"我返到屋企 先得閒上嚟連登認真回覆<br />\n<br />\n想講連登好多係冷氣軍師<br />\n佢哋唔分享有用資訊 而係不斷指揮你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動千祈唔好聽連登講<br />\n自己試下現場討論<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e3cd14b10663623f925c3dc94d8f88cda4f33e3a","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"時辰一到全港大裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe31c02db972004797ce3a77a54663b3c0354b8","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"停一停諗一諗"},{"pid":"2e61841323dbab050e9aa5a9b3e4713873cb97aa","tid":1630291,"uid":56394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0636642cb32a7f0ae54d922ed1dbc58f4fd61fd","tid":1630291,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95296fa4c5536c6484a7c659908bdfc1fbfa6da7","tid":1630291,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"人權法全部係美中博弈利益考量，勇武再升級都唔關事，唔好天真嚇自己，美國人係帶槍上街，唔需要顧慮勇武是否過頭，答案係唔會。記唔記得，和你飛時候一個鬼佬都講過，'dont say what happened, we know what happened, say what you want.'"}]}